name: THE TICKLE - Issue #36
description:
Art zine focused on NFT artists and creative writers.

Issue #36 features artists Linda Loh ( @__lindaloh__ ), Saeko Ehara ( @Sko_hr ) & Loren Bednar ( @LorenBednar ), with writing by Sabrin Hasbun ( @HasbunSabrin )

Created by artists Wily Guys ( @guyswily ) & Theo Horsmeier ( @THorsmeier ) and writer Joanne Rush ( @JonicolaRush ).
